{
  "title": "ISic003150. Epitaph of Quintus Pompeius Sosius Clementianus",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>D(is) m(anibus) s(acrum) <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Quinto · Pompeio · Sosio\n                    Clementiano\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quinto\">Q(uinto)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Pompeio\">Pompeio</span> · Sosio <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Clementiano\">Cl<span class=\"apex\" title=\"apex over: e\">é</span>mentiano</span></span> · <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>filio · et infanti <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>dulcissimo · qui vixit <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>mensib(us) · VII · dieb(us) · X<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">X͡V</span>III <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>parentes </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>DMS<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Quinto · Pompeio · Sosio\n                    Clementiano\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quinto\">Q</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Pompeio\">POMPEIO</span>·SOSIO<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Clementiano\">CL<span class=\"apex\" title=\"apex over: e\">é</span>MENTIANO</span></span>·<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>FILIO·ETINFANTI<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>DULCISSIMO·QUIVIXIT<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>MENSIB·VII·DIEB·X<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">X͡V</span>III<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>PARENTES</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003150_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\" src=\"ISic003150_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003150.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\" src=\"ISic003150-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003150_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\" src=\"ISic003150_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003150_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\" src=\"ISic003150_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Prag from photograph</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>The F of infanti has a substantial foot, giving the appearance of an E (visual confusion between these letters not uncommon in C2-C3 inscriptions); the A of infanti lacks a cross-bar.</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. To Quintus Pompeius Sosius Clementianus, son and sweetest newborn, who lived for 7 months and 28 days, erected by his parents</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Given that Biscari undertook excavations at Centuripe, and that the family of the Pompeii Sosii has part of its origin in Centuripe, it is at least as possible that the stone comes originally from Centuripe as from Catania. It seems most likely that Clementianus is the son of a freedman of the family.</p>  <p>Korhonen's suggestion that the apices/interpuncts in line 6 serve to indicate abbreviations cannot stand given that the sign appears after the numeral VII also, so they serve simply to separate all elements on the line, as is typical.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li>  <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">06.24510</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li><li></li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buch/4004\" target=\"_blank\">1088*.282</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001137</a></li><li> Korhonen 2004 13 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>V-cut letters of slightly irregular module and height, with pronounced serifs. Interpuncts are above the line and not clearly distinguishable from apices</p> Line 1-7  17-21  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
